<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT20">
<l>vāṉavar taṅkaḷ kōṉum malarmicai yayaṉum nāḷum</l>
<l>tēmalar tūvi yēttuñ cēvaṭic ceṅkaṇ mālai</l>
<l>māṉavēl kaliyaṉ coṉṉa vaṇṭamiḻ mālai nālaint</l>
<l>ūṉama tiṉṟi vallā roḷivicum pāḷvar tāmē .</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who flawlessly master this garland of four-[times-]five fine Tamil verses</l>
<l>Composed by Kaliyaṉ with a proud spear, to red-eyed Māl with rosy feet</l>
<l>[Where] the king of the celestials and the Unborn on the blossom</l>
<l>Praise [him] and daily scatter honeyed blooms, they will rule the bright heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
